sample_data_processing: Illumina software used for basecalling., Sequenced reads were mapped to hg38 genome using STAR two-pass alignment and gencode v32, Gene counts were done with ht-seq using parameters -s reverse -r pos -t exon -i gene_name -f bam, hg38, rmatrix of raw gene counts per sample, table of all non-promoter peaks with their gene links
